These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, mango
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, rowing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person eating mango##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | mango   | pomegranate  |
| Sport   | swimming | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, grapes
2 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the frog is not the person eating grapes##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | kiwi | grapes      |
| Pet    | frog  | goldfish |

 #################################

 
