.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, potato
2 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig
1. the person eating potato is not the owner of the turtle##6
2. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | strawberry  | potato |
| Pet    | turtle | guinea-pig    |

